{
  "stem": "7093.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I just felt I couldn't work with children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I made an exam.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I did, did some evening classes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I made an exam.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I got into the Minister of Finance as a filing clerk and worked there and worked my way up, and eventually got a so-called flat.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I thought I could bring him home quite soon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The flat were two ex-prison cells with barred, with barred windows, and iron doors, and, and, and scorpions, and no light, and no, no water.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But otherwise, it was perfect.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And eventually, I got light and water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then I thought I could get Ilan in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then came the news that my husband, who-- I had a, a letter from the hospital where he was that he is incurable.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And suddenly, he recovered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "During an insulin [INAUDIBLE], he suddenly recovered.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And, and he was playing again in the orchestra.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But he was very upset that we weren't there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Now, I wasn't going to live with him anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "That was over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I, again, started my divorce proceedings in Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But I said, well, he is the father of the child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I took six months' leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I let my flat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I went to South Africa with Ilan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And I found that he was very happy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I wanted to go back, except that the person I, I sold-- I, I let my flat to who was an old [INAUDIBLE] friend from [INAUDIBLE] sold my flat.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I would have had to go back to the [INAUDIBLE] again, to, to the hostel again, and live with three other women and put the child into a home.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I decided I'm not doing it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "So I couldn't go back to Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
